title: Spectrum PCMB - December 2015 (gnv64)
description:
This torrent contains December issues of the monthly academic magazine SPECTRUM for 4 subjects viz. physics, chemistry, biology & maths. They are meant for class XII science students preparing to appear for competitive entrance exams like IIT-JEE or AIPMT to gain entry into professional colleges (engineering, medical, para-medical etc.)

1. Spectrum Physics - December 2015 (100 pages, 10.7 mb)
2. Spectrum Chemistry - December 2015 (100 pages, 10.7 mb)
3. Spectrum Mathematics - December 2015 (100 pages, 13 mb)
4. Spectrum Biology - December 2015 (100 pages, 18.5 mb)
